				<wikidot:authorName>Torrence</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1420816</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'd like to give this a +1, but there are a number of verb tense issues here. For example, a description of a past event starts with past tense and then goes to present tense. There's also some odd phrasing, e.g. &quot;It was found with the following sign which was tied to a nail on the door that is written in Old Russian&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
